SUMMARY:Texas Health Catalyst Roundup and Rodeo
LOCATION:Capital Factory
DESCRIPTION:Join Dell Medical School’s Office of Innovation and Entrepreneu
 rship for a Texas-sized innovation event where teams from across UT will s
 howcase their entrepreneurial projects alongside key players in the local 
 life sciences community. Learn about evolving projects that seek unique bi
 omedical solutions to health challenges and network with innovators within
  Austin’s life science entrepreneurial ecosystem. This spring\, the challe
 nge was to address dementia\, neurodegeneration and the future of brain he
 alth. Finalists present their projects that answer the challenge\, and Tex
 as Health Catalyst program alumni give updates on their entrepreneurial jo
 urneys. Register to attend »\\n\\nRegister to attend »: http://www.eventbr
 ite.com/e/texas-health-catalyst-roundup-rodeo-spring-2026-tickets-19825175
 62397\\n\\nEvent page: https://dellmed.utexas.edu/events/texas-health-cata
 lyst-roundup-and-rodeo-043026
